  "title": "Latest Innovations in Azure Confidential Computing",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael geeks out with guests Vikas Bhatia (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/vikascbhatia/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>) and Run Cai (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/run-cai-36361b13/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>) about some of the recent announcements about Azure Confidential Computing.\n                        Most importantly, the recent release of Azure Confidential Computing VMs from AMD.\n                        <br><br>\n      \n                        <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                        <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/560700?theme=light class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/560700/>CC</a></iframe>\n      \n                        <h5>Links</h5> \n                        <!-- Links to news articles -->\n                        <ul>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/560700/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-pencil\"></i></a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/azure-confidential-computing/latest-innovations-in-azure-confidential-computing/ba-p/3573389\">Latest innovations in Azure confidential computing</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/theme/confidential-computing/\">Confidential Computing (Microsoft Research Cambridge)</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/solutions/confidential-compute/#overview\">Azure confidential computing</a></li>\n                    